name: Manhattan Life
description:
When I had live in New York the first week I remember felt completely lost in the city. NYC is easy but in the same time huge so the firsts weeks I had a lot of information in my mind but it wasn´t organized if in this time I would have had an app with the most famous buildings icons in the each area, the experience in the city would have been better.


That is the reason for the icons creation from Manhattan for free use for everyone needs it for differents uses to locate neighborhoods in Manhattan.
